<!DOCTYPE html>


<title>Half Your Age Rule!</title>

<h1>Half Your Age Rule!</h1>

<p> Do you think you're dating someone way younger? <br> Do you feel like
a creep when you go out to dinner? <br> let's see if you are one!</p>


<script>
let age = prompt("How old are you?");
let partnerAge = prompt("How old is your partner?");

if (age < 18)
  alert("You're too young to use this!");


age = (age / 2) + 7;

if (age > partnerAge)
  alert("Dude, you're way too old.")
else
  alert("You're alright, man");
</script>
















</html>
